resources.string: Download og installer yderligere funktioner til LED View Cover. Du kan oprette dine egne LED-ikoner og angive dem som dine meddelelsesikoner. Hvis du vil downloade dem senere, skal du gå til Indstillinger > Avancerede funktioner > Tilbehør > LED View Cover, og derefter vælge Download yderligere funktioner.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
